%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
%
%        BARYON ASYMMETRY OF THE UNIVERSE: SUPPLY AND DEMAND  
